        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "授與大威光大菩薩雙手掌中。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸如來。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即為立名號金剛光。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以金剛光灌頂法而為灌頂。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時金剛光菩薩摩訶薩。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即以所授金剛日相。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普遍照耀一切如來。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說此頌曰。",
        "from": "T18n0882_002:0345a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　此是一切大覺尊　　能破一切無智闇　於微塵數日光中　　此日光明勝增上爾時世尊復入寶幢大菩薩三昧。",
